The <code><pre> ... </pre></code> Tags wrapping the tables sections below are there for if you want to copy and paste to disqus comments.
The Tags will format a lined up table

Please note you will see some colour highlighting because disqus thinks it is computer code.
See https://help.disqus.com/en/articles/1717236-syntax-highlighting for a better explanation

The way the scores are calculated is described at https://github.com/kaptainkarl/f1-predictor/blob/master/docs/algorithms_description.txt




